OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FAbigail works to persuade
OL,7,     FMackenzie. Richie's day goes from
OL,8,     Fbad to worse. Alf's unable to
OL,9,     Fenjoy the win.
OL,10,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,11,     FThe doctors and nurses at the
OL,12,     Fpractice take measures to minimise
OL,13,     Fthe over-prescription and overuse
OL,14,     Fof antibiotics in the face of a
OL,15,     Flooming crisis.
OL,16,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,17,     FTwo critically ill children are
OL,18,     Frushed in by ambulance within ten
OL,19,     Fminutes of each other.
OL,20,     FTen-year-old Kai has been having
OL,21,     Fseizures, and 18-month-old Joel is
OL,22,     Fstruggling to breathe.
