OL,5,G2100 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,7,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,8,     Fpassengers. A man suffers brain
OL,9,     Fdamage after falling from a wall.
OL,10,     FA young cyclist endures a
OL,11,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
OL,12,G2200 999: Critical Condition
OL,13,     FMatthew is rushed into hospital
OL,14,     Fafter a collision between his
OL,15,     Fmotorbike and a tractor. His chest
OL,16,     Fhas taken the full force of the
OL,17,     Fimpact but there could be other,
OL,18,     Fhidden injuries.
